<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Hosting Controller Support</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.7.2/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }
        .sidebar {
            width: 250px;
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: #ecf0f1;
        }
        .sidebar .nav-link {
            color: #ecf0f1;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .sidebar .nav-link:hover, .sidebar .nav-link.active {
            background-color: #34495e;
            transform: translateX(5px);
        }
        .sidebar-header {
            padding: 20px 15px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #34495e;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .sidebar-header img {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .sidebar-header h4 {
            color: #ecf0f1;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .sidebar-header p {
            color: #bdc3c7;
            margin-bottom: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .main-content {
            flex-grow: 1;
        }
        .card {
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }
        .card-header {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            border-bottom: none;
            border-top-left-radius: 10px;
            border-top-right-radius: 10px;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #3498db;
            border-color: #3498db;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #2980b9;
            border-color: #2980b9;
        }
        .gradient-custom {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3498db, #2980b9);
        }
        .contact-info-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .contact-info-icon {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-right: 15px;
            color: #3498db;
        }
        .faq-item {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .faq-question {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .faq-answer {
            color: #34495e;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="d-flex">
        <div class="sidebar">
            <div class="sidebar-header">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/80" alt="User Avatar">
                <h4>John Doe</h4>
                <p>Premium Plan</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="nav flex-column px-3">
                <li class="nav-item mb-2"><a class="nav-link rounded" href="dashboard.html"><i class="bi bi-speedometer2 me-2"></i>Dashboard</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item mb-2"><a class="nav-link rounded" href="#domains"><i class="bi bi-globe me-2"></i>Domains</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item mb-2"><a class="nav-link rounded" href="#email"><i class="bi bi-envelope me-2"></i>Email</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item mb-2"><a class="nav-link rounded" href="#databases"><i class="bi bi-database me-2"></i>Databases</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item mb-2"><a class="nav-link rounded" href="#files"><i class="bi bi-folder me-2"></i>File Manager</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item mb-2"><a class="nav-link rounded" href="settings.html"><i class="bi bi-gear me-2"></i>Settings</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item mb-2"><a class="nav-link rounded" href="billing.html"><i class="bi bi-credit-card me-2"></i>Billing</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item mb-2"><a class="nav-link active rounded" href="support.html"><i class="bi bi-question-circle me-2"></i>Support</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item mb-2"><a class="nav-link rounded" href="#logout"><i class="bi bi-box-arrow-right me-2"></i>Logout</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="main-content p-4">
            <h1 class="h3 mb-4">Support & Contact</h1>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="card mb-4">
                        <div class="card-header gradient-custom">
                            <h2 class="h5 mb-0">Contact Us</h2>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <form>
                                <div class="mb-3">
                                    <label for="name" class="form-label">Name</label>
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" required>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-3">
                                    <label for="email" class="form-label">Email</label>
                                    <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" required>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-3">
                                    <label for="subject" class="form-label">Subject</label>
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="subject" required>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-3">
                                    <label for="message" class="form-label">Message</label>
                                    <textarea class="form-control" id="message" rows="5" required></textarea>
                                </div>
                                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Send Message</button>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="card mb-4">
                        <div class="card-header gradient-custom">
                            <h2 class="h5 mb-0">Contact Information</h2>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <div class="contact-info-item">
                                <i class="bi bi-telephone contact-info-icon"></i>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="mb-0"><strong>Phone:</strong></p>
                                    <p>+1 (800) 123-4567</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="contact-info-item">
                                <i class="bi bi-envelope contact-info-icon"></i>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="mb-0"><strong>Email:</strong></p>
                                    <p>support@hostingcontroller.com</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="contact-info-item">
                                <i class="bi bi-clock contact-info-icon"></i>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="mb-0"><strong>Business Hours:</strong></p>
                                    <p>Monday - Friday: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM EST</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-header gradient-custom">
                            <h2 class="h5 mb-0">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <div class="faq-item">
                                <p class="faq-question">How do I reset my password?</p>
                                <p class="faq-answer">You can reset your password by clicking on the "Forgot Password" link on the login page and following the instructions sent to your email.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="faq-item">
                                <p class="faq-question">How can I upgrade my hosting plan?</p>
                                <p class="faq-answer">To upgrade your hosting plan, go to the Billing section and click on the "Upgrade Plan" button. Choose your desired plan and follow the prompts to complete the upgrade process.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="faq-item">
                                <p class="faq-question">What is your uptime guarantee?</p>
                                <p class="faq-answer">We offer a 99.9% uptime guarantee for all our hosting plans. If we fail to meet this guarantee, you may be eligible for account credits.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>